title: MFA Press Statement: Visit by Minister for Foreign Affairs Dr Vivian Balakrishnan to the Republic ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Republic of Singapore ) Minister for Foreign Affairs Dr Vivian Balakrishnan will be visiting New Delhi, India , to co-chair the Fourth Meeting of the India-Singapore Joint Ministerial Committee
